Who do I aspire to be
- One who does not compare one's circumstances/oneself with others
- One who is not overly affected by what others are doing, have done or will do
- One who acts and behaves according to one's own intuition and principles
- One who is always mindful of what one is doing and always steering oneself to achieve one's goals (small innocous decisions add up over time)
- One who does not balk at hard decisions/failure and has the courage to take what looks like the best action
- One who does not distract oneself with petty pleasures
- One who enjoys challenges and pursuits knowing that they will bring reward and knowledge
- One who does not bow down/open up/attempt to please or make sacrifice for others unless they have earned one's respect
- One who is not completely dependent on others for one's sense of fulfillment/worth
- Who pursues music relentlessly


