Personal transformation
Start from within kill anxiety and slowly start making changes in your life. Meditation is medicine, it's rehab, do it frequently and regularly
Take it slowly, step by step, doing too many things at once would just lead to failure, patience, belief

First step is to see things as they are without fear, longing
Let your calm true self be the one at the helm
Expectations weigh you down, you are fearful to work towards music because you feel too left behind and because you might fail
Bleed out your ego, anxiety and learn to submerge yourself in learning
Learn to be comfortable with failure, confusion.
Always remember why you are pursuing it, to learn for its sake and discovery
To slowly start fashioning sounds which are an expression of you

Trying to do something because you should (guilting?) has failed without exception
Pursue something solely for yourself because that is what will bring happiness
Believe in your choice, believe that it will lead you to a new experience, a new sensation and perhaps a new happiness
Believe in yourself, believe that you can walk that path, that you can overcome all doubt,distractions and obstacles


